  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Modeller",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Create accurate and organized Architectural Revit (BIM) models.</li>\n  <li>Develop plan, elevation, section, and detail drawings from the models with adequate detail and proper annotation for tender and construction.</li>\n  <li>Develop and maintain BIM standards and procedures for sheet layout, layering, modelling processes and drawing formats.</li>\n  <li>Work productively and coordinate activities on numerous projects concurrently.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work individually and as part of a team to meet deadlines.</li>\n  <li>Well versed in Revit/BIM software in Archi and Structure.</li>\n  <li>Conversant in Singapore Construction Industry regulation.</li>\n  <li>Manage process of coordination, exchange of data and collaboration of BIM with project stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate As-Built/Record Model</li>\n  <li>Facilitate the transfer of information on the file sharing exchange protocol</li>\n  <li>Perform QAQC on modelled elements to ensure quality</li>\n  <li>Ensure all exported information are recorded in the correct directory</li>\n  <li>Experience in drawing coordination and BIM management in Singapore Construction Industry.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Architecture/Engineering/ Construction, Specialist Diploma in BIM or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Excellent in Autodesk Revit Architecture, Structure, and Navisworks,</li>\n  <li>At least 3 Year(s) of relevant experience in C&amp;S, Architectural BIM Modeling related projects</li>\n  <li>Able to complete models, shop drawings in timely and quality manner</li>\n  <li>Excellent in managing Common Data environment for projects.</li>\n  <li>Good Knowledge of in Autodesk Construction Cloud (ACC Build) is of an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Excellent time management and communication skills.</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
